<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 18:15:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国比亚迪在墨西哥推出中型混合动力皮卡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-unveils-mid-size-hybrid-ev-pickup-mexico-2024-05-14/</link><description>中国汽车制造商比亚迪周二在墨西哥推出了Shark，这是一款中型混合动力电动皮卡，扩大了其在北美市场的立足点，这款车直接瞄准了现有的福特、通用汽车和丰田汽车公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 16:45:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-unveils-mid-size-hybrid-ev-pickup-mexico-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>由于化学品价格压力达到预期，Brenntag 股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brenntag-shares-fall-chemicals-price-pressures-hit-forecast-2024-05-14/</link><description>由于价格压力和某些地区的需求低于预期，德国化学品分销商 Brenntag 下调了年度盈利预期，且第一季度业绩未达预期，该公司股价周二大幅下跌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 14:53:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brenntag-shares-fall-chemicals-price-pressures-hit-forecast-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>斯瓦泰克常规赛战胜凯斯后进入意大利公开赛半决赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/swiatek-into-italian-open-semis-after-routine-win-over-keys-2024-05-14/</link><description>两届冠军伊加·斯瓦泰克周二以6-1 6-3战胜18号种子麦迪逊·凯斯，轻松进入意大利公开赛半决赛，并将对阵美国三号种子可可·高夫或中国选手郑钦文。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 14:27:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/swiatek-into-italian-open-semis-after-routine-win-over-keys-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普称美国需要对中国其他车辆和产品征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-us-china-tariffs-needed-other-vehicles-products-2024-05-14/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普周二表示，拜登政府对中国电动汽车、半导体和医疗产品征收的新关税应适用于其他类型的车辆和产品。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 13:31:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-us-china-tariffs-needed-other-vehicles-products-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>七国集团将讨论美国对中国加征关税后的全球贸易风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/g7-discuss-global-trade-risks-after-us-tariffs-china-2024-05-14/</link><description>意大利经济部长吉安卡洛·乔治蒂表示，七国集团（G7）主要民主国家下周将在意大利举行会议，讨论美国对中国征收“非常严厉”关税后全球贸易分裂的风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 13:16:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/g7-discuss-global-trade-risks-after-us-tariffs-china-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>总统就职前一周，台湾与中国的紧张局势加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-china-tensions-ratchet-up-week-before-presidential-inauguration-2024-05-14/</link><description>台湾报道称，随着台湾新总统就职前一周紧张局势加剧，中国军队周二在该岛附近进行了另一次“战斗巡逻”，包括派遣飞机穿越台湾海峡敏感的中线。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 13:14:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-china-tensions-ratchet-up-week-before-presidential-inauguration-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>中方强烈反对美加征关税 承诺采取措施维权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-strongly-opposes-us-tariff-hikes-pledging-measures-defend-rights-2024-05-14/</link><description>中国商务部周二表示，中方强烈反对美国加征关税，并表示将采取坚决措施捍卫自身权益。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 12:06:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-strongly-opposes-us-tariff-hikes-pledging-measures-defend-rights-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>解说：为什么新喀里多尼亚会发生反对法国投票改革的骚乱？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/why-are-there-riots-new-caledonia-against-frances-voting-reform-2024-05-14/</link><description>法国在南太平洋的海外领地新喀里多尼亚在巴黎立法者讨论了一项宪法修正案草案，允许新喀里多尼亚人在省级选举中投票后，该地区爆发了暴力事件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 11:54:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/why-are-there-riots-new-caledonia-against-frances-voting-reform-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国-海湾自由贸易谈判在沙特工业议程上陷入僵局</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-gulf-free-trade-talks-stall-saudi-industrial-agenda-sources-say-2024-05-14/</link><description>消息人士称，由于沙特阿拉伯担心廉价的中国进口商品可能会削弱其将沙特转变为工业强国的雄心，中国与阿拉伯集团之间的自由贸易协定谈判陷入僵局。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 11:08:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-gulf-free-trade-talks-stall-saudi-industrial-agenda-sources-say-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>中美电动汽车贸易战威胁拜登的清洁汽车议程</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-china-ev-trade-war-threatens-bidens-clean-car-agenda-2024-05-14/</link><description>拜登政府计划对中国电动汽车和电池征收新的高额关税，这将为美国汽车业就业提供暂时保护，但可能会损害白宫通过加速美国电动汽车普及来应对气候变化的努力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 11:02:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-china-ev-trade-war-threatens-bidens-clean-car-agenda-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>蚂蚁集团利润下降19%至78.7亿元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ant-group-profit-down-19-787-bln-yuan-2024-05-14/</link><description>根据路透社根据阿里巴巴集团控股公司周二发布的财报计算得出的数据，截至 12 月 31 日的三个月内，中国蚂蚁集团的净利润下降了 19%，为人民币 78.7 亿元（合 10.9 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 10:55:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/ant-group-profit-down-19-787-bln-yuan-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国阿里巴巴利润暴跌86%，但收入超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-alibaba-beats-quarterly-revenue-estimates-2024-05-14/</link><description>中国阿里巴巴集团周二公布第四季度利润暴跌 86%，主要是由于股权投资的估值变化，导致其在美国上市的股价在早盘交易中下跌近 6%，尽管营收超出预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 10:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-alibaba-beats-quarterly-revenue-estimates-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：通胀守夜看到个股余兴表演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-14/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 10:11:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国贸易主管建议提高关税以解决中国的“不公平”做法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-trade-chief-recommends-higher-tariffs-address-chinas-unfair-practices-2024-05-14/</link><description>美国贸易代表戴凯瑟琳周二建议对一系列中国商品征收更高的关税，并呼吁扩大执法力度，以解决中国持续损害美国工人和制造商的技术转让行动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 10:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-trade-chief-recommends-higher-tariffs-address-chinas-unfair-practices-2024-05-14/</guid></item><item><title>英国就香港间谍指控召见中国大使</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/britain-summons-chinese-ambassador-over-hong-kong-spying-charges-telegraph-2024-05-14/</link><description>英国外交部周二召见中国大使，表示在三名男子被指控为香港从事间谍活动后，英国境内的间谍活动和网络攻击是不可接受的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 10:01:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/britain-summons-chinese-ambassador-over-hong-kong-spying-charges-telegraph-2024-05-14/</guid></item></channel></rss>